0\" class=\"sword\">凶焰</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-xiong1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">xiōng</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-yan4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">yàn</a> ]: ferocity; aggressive arrogance</span>\n<hr>\n<div>\n  <div>\n    <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">臽</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">火</a></span> (fire) conveys the meaning.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div>HSK: 6</div>\n<div>Freq: 2259</div>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Chinese</span>: If there is a fire brewing under a pothole, a big flame might burst out at some point.</div>\n<hr>\n<div><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Meaning:</span> flame<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Story:</span> If there is a fire brewing under a pothole, a big flame might burst out at some point.<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Kind:</span> both<br><img src=\"lf_28976.gif\"></div>\n<div>\n  <hr>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description\">從「 火 」，「 臽 」聲，本義為火苗。北周庾信〈對燭賦〉：「光清寒入，燄暗風過。」 「 焰 」可表示照耀。北周庾信〈燈賦〉：「動鱗甲於鯨魚，燄光芒於鳴鶴。」 「 焰 」還表示燃燒。唐張讀《宣室志》卷六：「於是里人數輩，夜尋其光，俯而觀之，其光自土而出，若焰薪火。」 「 焰 」還可比喻氣勢。宋留元剛《＜顏魯公文集＞後序》：「觀所奏論事，先白長官之疏，嬰逆鱗，陵焰勢，抗言不忌。」</div>\n  <div id=\"humanum_full_description_en\">From the sound of \" fire\" and \" 臽\", the original meaning is flame. Northern Zhou Yuxin's \"Fu Zhu Fu\": \"Light and cold enter, flames and dark wind pass.\" \" Flame\" can mean shining. Bei Zhou Yuxin's \"Lamp Fu\": \"The moving scales are on the whale, and the flames are on the crowing crane.\" \" Flame\" also means burning. Tang Zhang read the sixth volume of \"Xuanshizhi\": \"So there are many generations, looking for the light at night, and looking down at it. The light comes out of the earth, like a fire.\" \" Flame\" can also be compared to momentum. Song Liuyuangang's \"《Anthology of Yan Lu Gong's Works》 After Preface\": \"Looking at what is played and discussing things, first of the chief Bai's scribbles, the 