ation rule explained <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br></p>\n          <p><b>Variant rule :</b> C672 &#x7130;&lt;&#x71C4;&gt;</p>\n          <p class=\"pre-inline\"><b>Variant rule clarification <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b><br>&#x7130; (raising flames) TW&#xD;&#xA;&#x71C4; &lt;weak flame&gt;</p>\n          <p><b>Applied rules <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p>\n          <p><b>New font rule <a target=\"_blank\"></a>:</b></p><a target=\"_blank\"><span></span></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"p-1 bg-primary col-md-9 col-sm-8 etymology-result\" id=\"etymologyCharacters\">\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known oracle characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known bronze characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p>There is no known seal characters found. 没.</p>\n        <hr>\n        <h3><span></span></h3>\n        <p></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>焰</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>焰<br>yàn<br>火光：光焰。<br>火苗：火焰。烈焰。气焰。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>焰</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［yàn］<br>［《廣韻》以贍切，去艷，以。］<br>亦作“焔1”。亦作“熖1”。亦作“燄1”。亦作“1”。“炎3”的被通假字。<br>(1)火苗。<br>(2)火光；辉光。<br>(3)照耀。<br>(4)燃烧。<br>(5)犹熏。<br>(6)比喻灼人的气势。参见“焰勢”。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>焰</span>字的英文翻译</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>◎ <b>焰</b><br>blaze, flame</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>焰</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【巳集中】【火字部】　焰； 康熙笔画：12； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0675.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页675第04</span></a><br>【廣韻】【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】?以贍切，音豔。【玉篇】光也。【廣韻】本作爓。【集韻】亦作炎。互詳炎，爓二字註。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>焰</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>焰</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：指兴旺发达，如焰头；也指火光，辉光，比喻气势，如气焰逼人。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">flame<br>Basic explanation of words<br>flame<br>yàn<br>Fire light: light flame.<br>Flame: flame. Flames. arrogance.<br>flame<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［yàn］<br>[\"Guang Yun\" cuts with support, goes to Yan, with. ]<br>Also known as \"焔1\". Also known as \"熖1\". Also known as \"Flame 1\". Also known as \"1\". \"Yan 3\" was passed falsely.<br>(1) Flames.<br>(2) Fire light; glow.<br>(3) Shine.<br>(4) Burning.<br>(5) Still smoked.<br>(6) Metaphor of scorching momentum. See \"Flame\".<br>flame<br>English translation of words<br>◎ Flame<br>blaze, flame<br>flame<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Si Collection] [Fire Word Department] 　yan; Kangxi Strokes: 12; Page Number: Page 675 04<br>[Guang Yun] [Ji Yun] [Rhyme Meeting] [Positive Rhyme]? Cut with 財, the sound is colorful. [Jade articles] Light also. [Guang Yun] This is a 爓. [Ji Yun] also for inflammation. Mutual details of inflammation, note the word 爓.<br>flame<br>Source glyph<br>flame<br>Name meaning<br>: Refers to prosperity, like the head of a flame; also refers to fire, radiance, metaphorical momentum, such as arrogance.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148276149883843.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148276149883843.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148276149883843.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">型<br>用<br>焰<br>形声字。火表意,其形像火苗溅出火星儿,表示火焰;角(xian)表声,省像人掉入陷阱,表示火焰是危险能伤人的。本<br>义是火苗。<br>火苗:一火「烈~ 「气~。<br>~口 ~心<br>yàn<br>爱~ 炽~ 敌~ 光~ 火~<br>~~<br>势~ 凶~ 光~万丈<br>焰焰<br>隶</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">тип<br>использовать<br>пламя<br>Пиктофонетические символы.<br>Огонь означает, что его изображение похоже на пламя, вырывающееся из искр, что означает пламя; рога (сянь) звучат так, как будто люди попадают в ловушки, что означает, что пламя опасно и может причинить людям вред.<br>Первоначальное значение - пламя.<br>Пламя: Огонь \"Яростный ~\" Ци ~.<br>~ рот ~ сердце<br>Любовь ~ Чи ~ Враг ~ Свет ~ Огонь ~<br>~~<br>Потенциал ~ свирепый ~ свет ~ десять тысяч футов<br>Пламя<br>писец</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">yàn</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div>1) пламя, языки огня</div>\n  <div>2) порыв, запал; душевная сила; величие (<i>человека</i>)</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=焰\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=焰&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=焰\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=焰\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=焰\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/焰\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=焰\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/焰\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=焰&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#焰\">Char lookup site</a></p>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"火","pinyins":["Huo3","huo3"]},{"glyph":"臽","pinyins":["xian4"]}],"isMentionedAt__hanziyuan_without_charactersWithComponent":["燄"]}